{"arkId":"cl010114791","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010114791","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1650 - 1675","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1650,"endYear":1675,"imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10066","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ovale  avec un double couvercle. Le couvercle du fond ajour\u00e9 d\u0027une rosace est d\u00e9cor\u00e9 d\u0027une frise niell\u00e9e compos\u00e9e de rinceaux, d\u0027animaux et de deux figures nues, la lunette du verre est d\u00e9cor\u00e9e de fa\u00e7on identique avec deux chiens, un dieu barbu et une repr\u00e9sentation de Diane. Le cadran en argent niell\u00e9 et \u00e9maill\u00e9 pr\u00e9sente un d\u00e9cor floral avec un oiseau en \u00e9mail translucide. Double cercle horaire \u00e0 chiffres romains et arabes. Le pourtour du cadran est orn\u00e9 d\u0027un d\u00e9cor de rinceaux fleuris niell\u00e9s.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; H SORE (mouvement)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6,7","displayDimension":"6,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"5","displayDimension":"5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,9","displayDimension":"2,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"no